articles.description: Landry Shamet scored 16 points in just 23 minutes as No. 22 Wichita State cruised to a 95-74 win over UConn on Saturday night.
articles.headline: No. 22 Wichita State routs UConn 95-74

images.caption: 11 players score for the No. 22 Shockers in a 95-74 home victory against the Huskies.
images.name: Wichita State too much for UConn

articles.description: His 3-pointer to beat No. 3 Purdue in a tense B1G matchup gave Miles Bridges and No. 4 Michigan State a signature victory and kept title hopes alive.
articles.headline: Miles Bridges rises to the moment for Michigan State

images.caption: Miles Bridges' 20 points Saturday included the 3-pointer that gave Michigan State its eighth consecutive victory.
images.name: Purdue vs. Michigan State (Miles Bridges) [576x324] - Copy

articles.description: Jermaine Marrow totaled 27 points, six rebounds and six assists to lead Hampton to an 82-52 wire-to-wire victory over Norfolk State on Saturday.
articles.headline: Marrow leads Hampton to 82-52 romp over Norfolk State

articles.description: Virginia Tech's Justin Robinson says his team's mentality is always to never give up which helped them upset No. 2 Virginia.
articles.headline: Robinson credits Coach Williams for mentality
